data.name: Currency-Universe
data.description: The currency converter is a software application or website that provides for the easy conversion of currency values based on present-day exchange rates. Such currency converters can easily be found for free on the Internet, and can quickly convert the value of one currency to another, such as dollars to euros, or euros to pounds, and back again. Currency conversion is of practical use to tourists who travel abroad, to businesses who do business overseas or are involved in imports and exports, and to FX traders.

data.description: Hangman is a paper and pencil guessing game for two or more players. One player thinks of a word, phrase, or sentence and the other(s) tries to guess it by suggesting letters within a certain number of guesses.
